main event: The Shene man sighting of a UFO took place in late July to early August 1955.
interesting points: The UFO was observed at tree top level with an estimated altitude of 60 to 100 feet., The sighting was documented by Project Blue Book., The document includes two photographs showing the rural landscape., The larger photograph shows a building in the distance., The smaller photograph depicts trees and power lines against the sky.
witness description: The details encounter references a sighting by a man named Shene but does not list confirmed witnesses.
